Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.58,0:00:05.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:08.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I bring you marvelous illusions that \Nmake this town sparkle at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:12.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy the miracle that is going \Nto happen under the moonlight tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:17.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:20.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.91,0:00:23.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-I have an alibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.22,0:00:27.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You claim that when the crime occurred,\N three days ago at 1:00 pm,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:31.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,you were on Mt. Takao.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.81,0:00:34.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You have a souvenir photograph with a \Nclock in the background to back it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:41.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,However, this photo was \Ntaken at 3:44:58.22 pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:43.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The clock had been messed with.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.05,0:00:47.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The length of the shadows \Nindicates the correct time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.52,0:00:57.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Everything has come to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.02,0:01:02.52,Signs - readability,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}The famous detective is just back from London, \Nbut has already solved a case!\NThere it is! His famous line: \N"Everything has come to light."\NShould Kid the Phantom Thief watch his back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.52,0:01:06.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"Everything has come to light," my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.06,0:01:08.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He won't stop with that arrogant catchphrase!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.89,0:01:10.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I bet you're looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.64,0:01:12.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The showdown between him and Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:14.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:17.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who's gonna \Nhave a showdown with Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.71,0:01:20.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-Inspector! There's a new \Nadvance notice from Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.66,0:01:22.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:57.39,Signs - Thief Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}A Great Detective Comes to Light
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:03:03.06,Signs,,0,0,0,,The Great Pecasso Exhibition  {sic}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:12.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So that's {\i1}Adam's Smile{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:15.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,They sure are handling it with care.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:18.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Little do they know that \NI'm gonna steal it tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:23.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Inspector Nakamori must be \Nresponsible for this tight security.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:27.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But not even Buddha realizes \Nthat I'm observing them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:29.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,from way over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:32.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The culprit is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:36.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Everything has come to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Aoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.43,0:03:41.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What, you don't know that famous tagline?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:44.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about the famous detective \Nwho just got back from London.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:46.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What the hell do I care about that crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:49.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Paris, London, or wherever,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:52.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna humor you playing detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:55.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Excuse me? You're the one \Nwho invited me here, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.87,0:03:58.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Only because the expression on your face \Nwas practically begging me to invite you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:00.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I didn't make that kind of face!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:02.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's your problem, Kai-troll?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:06.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.93,0:04:19.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So is this why you said the rink's condition \Nwas bad today and clung to the wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:20.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:24.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Say "Aoko-sama, please,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:26.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and I'll give you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:30.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-I'm never gonna beg you like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:37.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Aoko-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You should've said it sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:45.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:49.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Jii-chan's info better be on the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:56.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,While searching for information on \Nthe Big Jewels, as you requested,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:58.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I came across something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:00.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is a painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:04.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Young Master, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:08.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Adam's Smile{\i0} is definitely a \Nmasterpiece of abstract art.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:13.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But it's valued at 400 million, \Nwhich doesn't quite add up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:14.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:22.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The prevailing view is that Pecasso used \Na special kind of paint for this part,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:26.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but there's actually more to it than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:31.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:36.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief said he'd be here\N at 10:00 pm on the dot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:38.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All right, synchronize your watches.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:41.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's see, right now, it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:43.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,2015 CE.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:45.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,February 3rd, Tuesday,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:50.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,8:50:16.05 pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:54.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,My watch is never off more \Nthan 0.001 seconds in a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:56.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,For your information.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:59.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Y-You're the guy that just \Ngot back from London...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm Hakuba Saguru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:07.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Get lost! This is no place for amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:09.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shoo! Shoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:11.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Come now, Nakamori-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:13.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't be such a hard-ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:16.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,C-Commissioner Hakuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:21.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's my son. Unfortunately, all this \Nmedia adulation has gone to his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:26.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm hoping you'll show him up here so he \Nlearns just how tough a crime scene can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:30.87,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,In that case, leave it to me, Nakamori Ginzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:32.69,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There's my great inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:37.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If you've got any questions, \Nfeel free to ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:39.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:41.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What is Kid the Phantom Thief's gender?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:45.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,M-Male, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:46.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How old is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,When was he born?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:51.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's his blood type?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:52.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What type of women does he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.17,0:06:56.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What kind of cologne does he wear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:56.25,Signs,,0,0,0,,Favorite cologne?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:57.29,Signs,,0,0,0,,Height?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:57.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How tall is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:58.71,Signs,,0,0,0,,Weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:06:58.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How much does he weigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:00.09,Signs,,0,0,0,,Body type?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.95,0:07:00.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's his body type?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:01.13,Signs,,0,0,0,,Hairstyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:04.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's his hairstyle? His hobbies? \NHis favorite baseball team?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:02.55,Signs,,0,0,0,,Hobbies?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.55,0:07:04.35,Signs,,0,0,0,,Favorite baseball team?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:06.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-I dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:08.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:17.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The snow's really comin' down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:21.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I hate workin' when it's freezing like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.49,0:07:24.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then why not take a nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:32.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sweet dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:37.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The place is swarming with cops...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:38.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:41.26,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:44.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Get where you're supposed to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:45.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:48.02,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Slacker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:50.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:00.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A police badge?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:10.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:14.36,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.89,0:08:37.07,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What the hell?! What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:40.69,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1)}I took the painting.\N- Kid the Phantom Thief
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:41.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:43.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He must still be in the vicinity!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:45.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:49.58,Signs,,0,0,0,,I took the painting.\N- Kid the Phantom Thief
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:49.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:54.09,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, should I really take {\i1}Adam's Smile{\i0} now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:04.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Still, I'm surprised they fell \Nfor such a simple trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:05.11,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.91,0:09:08.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It was an extremely elementary trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:11.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,When something isn't where \Nit's supposed to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:13.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,people assume that it's disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:15.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's a sensory trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:19.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Not even magic shows use them these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:23.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're one minute, 13.02 seconds late,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:25.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:29.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, I got held up by the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:36.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It seems you weren't so quick on \Nthe uptake with this trick, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:39.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. I cut your rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:40.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:44.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,After the magic show, did you \Nintend to perform a circus act?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:46.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Also,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:49.99,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I set free the ad balloon \Nthat was on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:51.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:55.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You've got no escape route now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:59.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief, \Ntrue identity unknown,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:02.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,it's time for everything \Nabout you to come to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:11.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Secrets{\i0} are everything to a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:14.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And I won't let mine come \Nto light that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.79,0:10:16.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A hang glider...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.89,0:10:19.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Just like Batman...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.67,0:10:22.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Batman is a comic book hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:23.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He doesn't really exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:24.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:27.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:30.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's a north by northwest wind tonight,\N seven on the wind scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.56,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Not conducive to night flights...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.91,0:10:38.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Damn that Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:42.19,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,K-Kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:43.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:44.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.44,0:10:49.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The skating rink!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:51.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:53.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Son of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:57.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,H-He split into two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:11:00.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-Which is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:02.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,On the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:05.61,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There's no way Kid would \Nbe terrible at skating!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:07.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:11.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This saves me, but I'm not \Nreally happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:13.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You're under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:17.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh? A balloon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.85,0:11:22.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,"Kid the Phantom Thief \Nis bad at ice skating."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:29.66,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What happened to your \Ngreat detective fresh from London?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:32.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,In the end, Kid got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:32.79,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief Steals Adam's Smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:35.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Put that away already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:39.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,February 4th, 2015.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:42.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,At 9:32.41,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:45.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I transfered here from \Na high school in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:47.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Th-That way of speaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.05,0:11:49.05,Signs,,0,0,0,,Hakuba Saguru
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.05,0:11:49.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm Hakuba Saguru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:51.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Everything will come to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:54.06,Signs,,0,0,0,,Hakuba Saguru
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:54.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:55.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:12:01.40,Signs,,0,0,0,,Blue Parrot
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:14.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wow! Hidden treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:20.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Not a winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:26.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's unfortunate, but don't look \Nso disappointed, Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:30.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't forget my poker face, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:33.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,So is everything ready for \Nthe next one, Jii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:36.14,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:51.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid will be on TV tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:56.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hear? Kid the Phantom Thief \Nwill be live on TV tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:59.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's awesome! I've gotta record it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:02.75,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief's \Nscene of the crime on live TV
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:03.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Broadcasting live, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:06.38,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I get more good luck as \Na robber than I deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:08.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Morning, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.17,0:13:09.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:14.43,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Recently, I entered a contest to try to win \NAround the World concert tickets!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:16.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And what do you think happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:18.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Y-You won, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.89,0:13:20.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:22.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A pair of tickets!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:27.90,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Your face totally gives it away, dingbat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.90,0:13:31.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?! Talk to me like that,\N and I won't invite you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:34.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It seems you're in a spot \Nof trouble, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:36.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,H-Hakuba-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:40.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm 180 centimeters tall. \NI weigh 65 kilograms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:44.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I was born on August 29th, 1997.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:47.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm a Virgo. And if you don't\Nmind that I'm blood type A,{smp: originally "if you mind that I'm blood type A" which seemed like it was missing the "don't" but this could also be a mixed up rewrite, TC}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:50.37,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I would like to go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:14:00.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A man who thoughtlessly refuses an \Noffer from a lady isn't worthy of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:02.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:04.92,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You couldn't even catch Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:07.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A mediocre detective and a \Nmediocre inspector's daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.34,0:14:09.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You deserve each other! {smp: and also you are a poopyhead!}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:12.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:16.86,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Apparently, he's partial to Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:21.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then let's do this. If I capture Kid tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:23.41,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,you invite me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:28.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:30.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If you catch Kid, let's go \Nto the concert together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:35.64,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Somebody like you is gonna catch the \Nunbeatable Kid the Phantom Thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.01,0:14:39.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Unlike you, Kid is a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:41.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It won't be an easy job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:46.31,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And if I do happen to lose, \NI'll leave escorting Aoko-kun to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.31,0:14:47.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:50.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna go to the concert,\N but you've got a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:07.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Look at all the guards here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:09.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector, this is it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:12.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The goddess statue that Kid \Nannounced he's going to steal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:14.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Steal it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:16.67,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There's no way he can!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:21.79,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Not even a rat could sneak \Nin here, let alone Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:23.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh? A rat...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:26.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Idiots! Catch that vermin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:27.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Your dad is in fine form, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:29.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.48,0:15:34.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And now, let's interview the detective who's \Nbeen in the spotlight lately, Hakuba-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.48,0:15:36.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Um, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:39.83,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Hakuba-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:42.54,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Just being conscientious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:46.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I've kind of got a personal stake\N in tonight's showdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.56,0:15:49.44,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Why, you... What an arrogant jackass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:51.34,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Watch me, you third-rate detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:55.32,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No way am I letting you go \Non a date with Aoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.55,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll have the last laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:02.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nothing in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:05.10,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nothing on the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:07.73,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nothing underground!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:12.01,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I guess even Kid can get scared off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:12.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:16.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How many guards are posted underground?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:19.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nobody's posted there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:22.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The basement's protected \Nby a myriad of sensors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:26.62,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Not even Kid is stupid enough \Nto try and get in that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:34.42,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:37.89,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:41.18,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But I've got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:43.68,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.26,0:16:50.65,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Bet they never figured I'd come up \Nthrough the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:53.23,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Four minutes left!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:55.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Will Kid really show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:56.94,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, Aoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:17:01.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Who are you rooting for?\N Hakuba-kun? Or Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:04.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,H-Hakuba-kun, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:07.95,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you sure? If he wins, you can't \Ngo to the concert with Kaito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:10.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-I don't need to go with {\i1}him{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:14.71,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,A mediocre detective and a mediocre \Ninspector's daughter! You deserve each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.48,0:17:18.29,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Why did he have to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:19.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.63,0:17:23.22,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.67,0:17:26.46,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The rest is just putting on \Nthe finishing touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:30.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This is as far as you get, \NKid the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:32.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:34.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:37.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,why don't we lower the \Ncurtain on this circus?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:39.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,S-Sleeping gas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:43.82,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I see. The circus finale is a smoke screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:49.93,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,In 17.58 seconds, this whole \Nroom will be filled with gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:52.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:54.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:56.58,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't know about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:00.57,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:03.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Just ten seconds away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.59,0:18:05.05,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:06.85,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,There's an interloper in the basement!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:08.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:10.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:11.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:15.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,He's 25 centimeters away from the mask,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:17.00,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm 20 centimeters away,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:18.98,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,and we're moving at the same speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:20.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:22.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:23.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:25.20,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:27.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:29.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kid? Aren't you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:29.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:31.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:31.15,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,{\a6}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:32.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:41.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspector, I caught Kid the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:44.72,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:47.97,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well done, Hakuba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:51.40,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Hakuba-kun, how did it feel to capture Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:54.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Actually, it was a cinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.12,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,What's that balloon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.48,0:19:06.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just... time for me \Nto make my getaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:09.81,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-Inspector! Kid isn't in the basement!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:11.24,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,It's Detective Hakuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.52,0:19:16.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,According to my calculations, I definitely \Nshould've reached it before him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.08,0:19:20.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,But he...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:27.63,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:32.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Then you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:35.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,...Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:41.77,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,K-Kid the Phantom Thief is impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.77,0:19:43.60,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I-It's Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:46.28,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief has appeared at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:48.78,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.78,0:19:50.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.95,0:19:54.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't move if I were you, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.43,0:19:58.25,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That's unusually menacing, coming from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:20:02.21,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Tonight's job is a little personal...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:04.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Personal? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.48,0:20:08.04,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be seeing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:15.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Just being conscientious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:18.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,That son of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:34.49,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,If this isn't what I'm looking for, \Nthen there's no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:35.91,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:49.01,Signs,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori Protects \Nthe Goddess Statue!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:51.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,You need to keep it stabilized.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:53.39,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:58.52,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Would you like more painkillers?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:21:01.08,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:06.16,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,All traces of the gas will be out of my body \Nin three hours, 31 minutes, and 49 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:07.33,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:12.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll get you for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:25.47,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,How boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.32,0:21:35.76,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Tonight's performance featured a thief \Nand a detective crossing swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:38.59,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Did you enjoy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:43.06,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, see you next illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.55,0:23:23.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The word "magician" has two meanings.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.17,0:23:24.75,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,The first is an illusionist,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.75,0:23:26.45,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,that is, an entertainer who performs tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.45,0:23:28.88,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,And the second is a wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.88,0:23:30.96,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Our class has a new student, Akako Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.96,0:23:33.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,She's totally beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.27,0:23:35.17,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but a little weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.17,0:23:37.03,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,This isn't Medieval Europe,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.03,0:23:38.84,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,but is she really a witch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.84,0:23:43.35,Signs,,0,0,0,,Scarlet Seduction
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.19,0:23:43.35,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Next time on {\i1}Magic Kaito 1412{\i0}:\N Scarlet Seduction!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.35,0:23:46.27,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Step right this way! Watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.27,0:23:48.80,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't miss the illusion!
